column3: The name can only contain between 2 and 32 characters. Only the following characters are allowed: 'a-z', 'A-Z', '0-9', space and other special characters (!"#$%'()*+,-./:;<=>?@[]^_{|}~) except &,` or $(
It must be a 12-digit number, cannot start with 0, and should contain only numbers.
It must match an existing AP group
Between -90 and 90, and contains a maximum of 6-digit decimal
Between -180 and 180, and contains a maximum of 6-digit decimal
